_sText:
Port from Counter-Strike: Global Offensive to Counter-Strike: Source, of Radix's famous map, de_austria. This port was made with Radix's indirect permission, provided by Nikosemen, who also provided the original VMF which I used to port and improve the map.

In-game map name: de_csgoaustria

Features:
- HDR and LDR compatible.
- Working radar
- Working soundscapes
- Working bot navigation (original CSGO file)
- Working custom particles (chimney smoke, etc)
- Working cubemaps
- Improved shadows

As it is, this port is identical to how it is in CSGO. No glitches or anything as far as I know, and no compromises. A perfect port.

Special thanks to Gondallez for writing a particle converter.
